<p class="">There was an Amendment on the Order Paper, and I was unaware that my hon. Friend the Member for Norwood (Mr. Chamberlain) was not speaking to the Amendment.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
